This artwork is very special to me as it represents positive energy and luck.

You may wonder why I love generative art so much, and I believe this "Elementary luck 07" is the perfect example of my work and dedication.

Writing your own code as an artist gives you the freedom to do what you want as long as you have the patience, knowledge, and determination to achieve what you want. I don't consider luck as a passive event, but as something you provoke.
